# Makefile Quick Reference

## First Time Setup
make install          # Install mula package in editable mode

## Running Examples  
make run-dqn          # Train DQN on CartPole (300 episodes)
make run-dqn-long     # Train DQN on CartPole (500 episodes)
make run-dqn-render   # Train + watch with rendering
make run-dqn-demo     # Train longer + show results

## Quick Start
make quickstart       # Install + run example immediately

## Verification
make verify           # Check all dependencies are installed

## Development
make test             # Run tests
make lint             # Check code quality
make format           # Auto-format code
make clean            # Remove build artifacts

## Manual Commands
uv run python examples/dqn_cartpole.py --episodes 500 --seed 42
uv run python examples/dqn_cartpole.py --episodes 500 --render
uv run python examples/dqn_cartpole.py --episodes 100 --render-train

